    <text>
        <body>
            <head><name xml:lang="eng">Tunis</name></head>
            <div type="positioning">
                <p><geo>36.8, 10.18</geo></p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <table>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft"><hi rend="bold">Interrogatives</hi></cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">who?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Most commonly dialects show reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">man</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Who is this man? – He is my friend</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">škūn</hi> hā-ṛ-ṛāžil? – hūwa ṣāḥbi.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wer ist dieser Mann? – Er ist mein Freund.</cell>
                        <cell>من هذا الرجل؟هو صديقي.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">whose?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Whose car is this? – This is our car. It’s small but it’s
                            good.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">hāḏi kaṛhabt <hi rend="red">əškūn</hi>? – hāḏi l-kaṛhaba
                            mtāʕna. / hāḏi kaṛahbitna. hīya zġīra, āma / amma / lākin bāhya.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wessen Auto ist das? – Das ist unser Auto. Es ist klein, aber
                            gut.</cell>
                        <cell>هذه سيارة من؟هذه سيارتنا. هي صغيرة ولكنها جيدة.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">what?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, what are you doing now? – I’m watching TV.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">āš/š</hi>-ʕāmla taww(a), yā Fāṭma? – nitfarriž
                            f-it-talfza.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Fatima, was machst du gerade? – Ich schaue fern.</cell>
                        <cell>يا فاطمة، ماذا تفعلين الآن؟أشاهد التلفزيون/التلفاز.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">why?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">A very common pattern are reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">li
                                + ’ayy</hi> or <hi rend="italic">li + ’ayy + šay’</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Why didn’t he come? – I don’t know. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʕlāš</hi> ma-žā-š? – ma-naʕṛaf-š.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Warum ist er nicht gekommen? – Ich weiß es nicht.</cell>
                        <cell>لماذا لم يأتِ؟لا أعرف.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">A very common pattern are reflexes of CA <hi rend="italic">fī
                                + ’ayna</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where is my mobile (phone)? – Here it is!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">wīn</hi> il-buṛṭābil imtāʕi?- (a)hāwa hnā / hāw əhnā.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wo ist mein Handy? – Da ist es!</cell>
                        <cell>أين جوّالي (هاتفي النقال)؟ههنا!</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where to?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.) going? – I am going home.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">wīn</hi> māši / māšya? – māši / māšya l-id-dāṛ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wohin gehst du (f/m)? – Ich gehe nach Hause.</cell>
                        <cell>إلى أين تذهب؟ - تذهبين؟أذهب إلى البيت.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">where from?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where are you (m./f.; sg./pl.) from? – I am/ We are from
                            ….</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">mnīn</hi> inti / intūma? – āna / aḥna min …</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Woher bist du?/Woher seid ihr? – Ich bin aus… / Wir sind
                            aus…</cell>
                        <cell>من أين أنتَ – أنتِ؟ - أنتم؟أنا - نحن من.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">when?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, when did you see Muhammad? – I saw him yesterday. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">waqtāš</hi> rīt/šuft Muḥammad, yā Fāṭma? – rītu / šuftu
                            lbāraḥ / mbāraḥ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Fatima, wann hast du Muhammad gesehen? – Ich sah ihn
                            gestern.</cell>
                        <cell>يا فاطمة، متى رأيت محمدا؟رأيتُه أمس؟</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How are you (m./f.)? – I’m fine.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">šnūwa</hi> / <hi rend="red">šnīye</hi> ḥwālik? – lā
                            bās.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wie geht es dir (m/f)? – Mir geht es gut.</cell>
                        <cell>كيف حالكَ – حالكِ؟أنا بخير.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how much?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How much is half a kilo of lemons? – It’s 10 Pounds. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">b-qaddāš</hi> əṛṭal līmūn?- b-dīnāṛ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wieviel kostet ½ Kilo Zitronen? – Es kostet …</cell>
                        <cell>بكم نصف كيلو من الليمون؟ بـ...</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">how many?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How many children do you (f.) have? – I have two daughters
                            and three sons.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">qaddāš</hi> ʕandik ūlād? – ʕandi zūz bnāt w-tlāṯ(a)
                            ūlād.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wieviele Kinder hast du? – Ich habe zwei Töchter und drei
                            Söhne.</cell>
                        <cell>كم ولدا عندك؟عندي بنتان وثلاثة أبناء.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">which?</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">In which neighbourhood do you live? – We live in Zamalik. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">f-<hi rend="red">āni</hi> žīha / f-<hi rend="red">ānu</hi>
                            ḥayy tusuknu? – nusuknu fi Bāb Swīqa.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">In welchem Viertel/Bezirk wohnt ihr? – Wir wohnen in …</cell>
                        <cell>في أي حي تسكنون؟نسكن في...</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Demonstratives</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">this</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Who is this man? – He is my friend.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">škūn <hi rend="red">hā</hi>-ṛ-ṛāžil? – hūwa ṣāḥbi.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wer ist dieser Mann? – Er ist mein Freund.</cell>
                        <cell>من هذا الرجل؟هو صديقي.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Pronouns</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">I</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">I am a teacher.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Ich bin Lehrer.</cell>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Presentatives</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">there is … (m.)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where is my mobile? – Here is the phone!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">wīn il-buṛṭābil imtāʕi? – (a)hāwa <hi rend="red">hnā</hi> /
                            hāw <hi rend="red">əhnā</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wo ist mein Handy? – Hier ist es.</cell>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">there is … (f.)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Where is the car? – Here it is!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wo mist das Auto? – Hier ist es.</cell>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Adverbs</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">here</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">We have been here for 8 years.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ʕandna / ʕanna ṯmānya snīn <hi rend="red">hūni</hi> / əhnā. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wir sind seit 8 Jahren hier.</cell>
                        <cell>نحن هنا منذ 8 سنوات.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">now</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, what are you doing now? – I’m watching TV. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">āš/š-ʕāmla <hi rend="red">taww(a)</hi>, yā Fāṭma? –
                            nitfarriž f-it-talfza.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Fatima, was machst du gerade? – Ich schaue fern.</cell>
                        <cell>يا فاطمة، ماذا تفعلين الآن؟أشاهد التلفزيون/التلفاز.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">today</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">It’s very hot today.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">id-dinya sxūna baṛša <hi rend="red">l-yūm</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Heute ist es sehr heiß.</cell>
                        <cell>الطقس حار جدا اليوم.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">yesterday</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Yesterday it rained.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ilbāraḥ</hi> / <hi rend="red">imbāraḥ</hi> ṣabb
                            li-mṭaṛ</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Gestern regnete es.</cell>
                        <cell>أمس كان يهطل المطر.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">tomorrow</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Hey kids, tomorrow you have to study.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">yā ūlād, <hi rend="red">ġudwa</hi> yilzimkum taqṛāu.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Kinder, morgen müßt ihr lernen.</cell>
                        <cell>يا شباب، غدا عليكم أن تدرسوا.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">last year</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Last year we had many problems.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">il-ʕām illi fāt</hi> / <hi rend="red">ʕāmnāwal</hi> kānit
                            ʕandna / ʕanna baṛša mšākil.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Letztes Jahr hatten wir viele Probleme.</cell>
                        <cell>السنة الماضية كان عندنا مشاكل كثيرة.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Numerals</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">eight</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">We have been here for 8 years. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ʕandna / ʕanna <hi rend="red">ṯmānya</hi> snīn hūni / əhnā. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wir sind seit 8 Jahren hier.</cell>
                        <cell>نحن هنا منذ 8 سنوات.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">eleven</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">What’s the time? It’s 11 o’clock.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">qaddāš il-waqt? – la-<hi rend="red">ḥdāš</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wie spät ist es? – Es ist 11 Uhr.</cell>
                        <cell>كم الساعة؟الساعة 11.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">twelve</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">They have 12 goats and 2 cows.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ʕandhum <hi rend="red">ṯnāš-in</hi> miʕza w-zūz bagṛāt /
                            bagaṛtīn.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Sie haben 12 Ziegen und 2 Kühe.</cell>
                        <cell>عندهم 12 ماعزة وبقرتان.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">eighteen</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">There are 18 new students in our class.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">famma <hi rend="red">ṯmunṭāš-in </hi>ṭālib ždīd f-il-qism
                            imtāʕna.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">In unserer Klasse sind 18 neue Studenten.</cell>
                        <cell>في صفّنا 18 طالبا جديدا.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Adjectives</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">good</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">How are you (m./f.)? – I’m fine.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">šnūwa / šnīye ḥwālik? – <hi rend="red">lā bās</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wie geht es dir (m/f)? – Mir geht es gut.</cell>
                        <cell>كيف حالكَ – حالكِ؟أنا بخير.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Colours</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">white</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">My husband wears a white shirt. We have a white
                            car.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ṛāžli lābis sūrīya <hi rend="red">bīḏ̣a</hi> w-āna lābsa rūba bīḏ̣a. ʕandna / ʕanna kaṛhaba <hi rend="red">bīḏ̣a</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Mein Mann trägt ein weißes Hemd und ich trage ein weißes
                            Kleid.</cell>
                        <cell>يلبس زوجي قميصا أبيض وأنا ألبس فستانا أبيض.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">black</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">I don’t like this black shirt. / car.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ma-nḥibb-əš hā-l-maryūl il-<hi rend="red">akḥal</hi>. /
                            hā-l-kaṛhaba l-<hi rend="red">kaḥla</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Dieses schwarze Hemd/Auto gefällt mir nicht.</cell>
                        <cell>لا يعجبني هذا القميص الأسود.لا تعجبني هذه السيارة السوداء.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">pink</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">My wife bought a pink shirt / bag.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">maṛti šrāt maryūl <hi rend="red">waṛdi</hi>. / sāk <hi rend="red">waṛdi</hi>. (maryūl f-ir-<hi rend="red">rose</hi>. / sāk
                                f-ir-<hi rend="red">rose</hi>.) </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Meine Frau hat ein rosa Hemd/eine rosa Tasche gekauft.</cell>
                        <cell>اشترت زوجتي قميصا ورديا وحقيبة وردية.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">grey</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">a grey wall/a grey bag</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ḥīṭ <hi rend="red">ərmādi</hi> / sāk <hi rend="red">ərmādi</hi> (ḥīṭ <hi rend="red">gris</hi>/ sāk <hi rend="red">gris</hi>)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">eine graue Mauer/graue Tasche</cell>
                        <cell>جدار رمادي حقيبة رمادية</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">orange</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">an orange shirt / car</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">maryūl <hi rend="red">buṛdgāni</hi> (maryūl f-il-<hi rend="red">orange</hi>)</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">ein oranges Hemd/Auto</cell>
                        <cell>قميص برتقالي – سيارة برتقالية</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Prepositions</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="italic">fi</hi> vs. <hi rend="italic">bi</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">There are 18 new students in our class.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">famma ṯmunṭāš-in ṭālib ždīd <hi rend="red">f</hi>-il-qism
                            imtāʕna.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">In unserer Klasse sind 18 neue Studenten.</cell>
                        <cell>في صفّنا 18 طالبا جديدا.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Important verbs</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to do</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Fatima, what are you doing now? – I’m watching TV.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">āš/š-<hi rend="red">ʕāmla</hi> taww(a), yā Fāṭma? –
                            nitfarriž f-it-talfza.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Fatima, was machst du gerade? – Ich schaue fern.</cell>
                        <cell>يا فاطمة، ماذا تفعلين الآن؟أشاهد التلفزيون/التلفاز.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to stay</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Stay a bit longer! – No, I don’t have time.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">uqʕud</hi> šwayya! – lā, mā-ʕandī-š waqt.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Bleib ein bißchen! Nein, ich habe keine Zeit.</cell>
                        <cell>ابقَ هنا قليلا!لا, ليس لديَّ وقت.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to speak</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Do you speak Arabic? – Just, a little.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">titkallim</hi> b-il-ʕarbi? – šwayya baṛka.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Sprichst du Arabisch? – Nur ein bißchen.</cell>
                        <cell>هل تتكلم العربية؟قليلا فقط.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to rain</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Yesterday it rained.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">ilbāraḥ/imbāraḥ <hi rend="red">ṣabb li-mṭaṛ</hi>.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Gestern regnete es.</cell>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to open</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Open the window!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ḥill</hi> iš-šubbāk!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Mach das Fenster auf!</cell>
                        <cell>افتح النافذة!</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to close</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Close the doors!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">sakkir</hi> il-bībān!</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Mach dieTüren zu!</cell>
                        <cell>أغلق الأبواب!</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to take</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">What did you take? – Nothing.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">šnūwa <hi rend="red">xḏīt</hi>? – ḥatta šayy / ḥāža.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Was hast du genommen?Nichts.</cell>
                        <cell>ماذا أخذت (معك)؟لم آخذ شيئا.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to give</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Did you give the letter to Ahmad? – Yes, I gave it to
                            him.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʕṭīt</hi>-ši ž-žwāb l-Aḥmad? – ʔayy, ʕṭīt-hū-lu.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Hast du Ahmad den Brief gegeben?Ja, ich habe ihn ihm
                            gegeben.</cell>
                        <cell>هل أعطيت أحمد الرسالة؟نعم، أعطيتُه إياها.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to see</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">The children saw a beggar behind our house.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">iz-zġāṛ <hi rend="red">šāfu</hi> ṭallāb wṛā dāṛna.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Die Kinder sahen einen Bettler hinter unserem Haus.</cell>
                        <cell>الأطفال رأوا شحّادا وراء بيتنا.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to want</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Do you (f.) want to drink tea or coffee? – Tea
                            please.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">tḥibb</hi> tušṛub qahwa walla tāy? – māḏā bīya tāy.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Möchtest du Tee oder Kaffee trinken?Tee, bitte.</cell>
                        <cell>هل تريد أن تشرب قهوة أو شايا؟أريد شايا، من فضلك.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to bring</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Bring me the big bottle, please! – I'm right with
                            you.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">žīb</hi>li d-dabbūza, b-ṛaḅḅi! – tfa<hi rend="tei-orth">ḏ̣ḏ̣</hi>aḷ.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Bring mir bitte die große Flasche!Hier bitte.</cell>
                        <cell>من فضلك، اجلب لي الزجاجة الكبيرة.تفضل!</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">to have</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">They have a lot of money, but they are bad people.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʕand</hi>hum baṛša flūs, āma amma / lākin hūma nās
                            xayba.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Sie haben viel Geld, aber sie sind schlechte Leute.</cell>
                        <cell>عندهم كثير من النقود ولكنهم ناس سيئون.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Phrasemes</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">since/for</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom">Many Arabic dialects use periphrastic constructions to render
                            English ‛since’.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">We have been here for 8 years.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">
                            <hi rend="red">ʕandna</hi> / <hi rend="red">ʕanna</hi> ṯmānya snīn hūni /
                            əhnā. </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdID">Wir sind seit 8 Jahren hier.</cell>
                        <cell>نحن هنا منذ 8 سنوات.</cell>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <cell rend="tdLeft">
                            <hi rend="bold">Nouns</hi>
                        </cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre"/>
                        <cell rend="tdRight"/>
                        <cell rend="tdID"/>
                        <cell/>
