                        <cell rend="tdLeft">a little</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdCom"/>
                        <cell rend="tdCentre">Do you speak Arabic? – Just, a little.</cell>
                        <cell rend="tdRight">titkallim b-il-ʕarbi? – <hi rend="red">šwayya</hi>
